data.title: 1802 Circle
data.meta_description: To honor and recognize donors for their continued support of West Point and the Corps of Cadets, West Point Association of Graduates offers membership to five distinct giving societies. Donors are recognized for generous annual gifts, planned or estate gifts, and lifetime cumulative giving to the Academy.
